Streamlit Production Implementation

python
import streamlit as st
import pandas as pd

st.title("📊 HR Salary Analytics")
df = pd.read_csv("employees.csv")

col1, col2, col3, col4 = st.columns(4)
col1.metric("Mean", f"₹{df['salary'].mean():,.0f}")
col2.metric("Median", f"₹{df['salary'].median():,.0f}")
col3.metric("Std Dev", f"₹{df['salary'].std():,.0f}")
col4.metric("Count", f"{len(df):,}")

st.dataframe(df.describe())
st.caption("Production HR: Instant insights for C-suite")

Descriptive stats = Executive language. Raw data → Boardroom insights in 10 seconds. 📈✅